data.description:
Discover the potential of this 1,700 square foot residence nestled on a spacious 2-acre lot. This captivating home, boasting 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, awaits a discerning buyer with a vision for restoration and customization. Embrace the opportunity to transform this property into your dream home, tailoring every detail to reflect your personal style. With ample space both indoors and outdoors, the canvas is set for you to create a residence that perfectly suits your lifestyle. Unleash your creativity and reimagine the possibilities within this charming abode. Seller is offering a $2500 flooring credit and a $500 paint credit. 
This home is being sold "as is condition".
